column1: # The January 1956 figure is identified as part-estimate on the sheet and has been retained.
# Figures for 1864 duplicate the 1864 figures for the Boston Bargate Lodge site, but they seem to belong to the Grand Sluice site and so have been retained.
# Two copies of the 1880s sheet are present in the Met Office volumes.
# The station continued until 1994 according to MIDAS.
